current ideas:
- single elderly living alone by measuring audio changes, sharp audio change -> detects a potential fall or for abuser
- petty theft for local supermarkets and mama shop, immediate notice / information when suspected theft, install into cameras

overall plan:
- to be able to detect elderly falling down in their homes with timely alerts to relevant parties

flow:
- a device that captures audio around the house -> sends data to an edge processing device
- edge processing device will determine whether it is a fall or not
- upon detection of a fall -> it will alert the relevant authorities

challenges:
- to make sure the program can be functional on small devices
- to be able to have the alerts be sent out no matter the network strength

notes:
- the device in charge of the recording audio and edge processing can be the same device
- LoRaWAN devices can be used to ensure reliability of sending out messages no matter network strength

